{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/limonada-pre-veraniega/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"A pizcas y a mizcas"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"1c60938a-be5e-5755-9898-e4ec6ced8252","excerpt":"Hace un par de semanas nos regalaron una bolsa de limones… de esos que no pasan por cámaras, ni ceras ni están sometidos a ningún tratamiento. Limones…","html":"<p>Hace un par de semanas nos regalaron una bolsa de limones… de esos que no pasan por cámaras, ni ceras ni están sometidos a ningún tratamiento. Limones ecológicos 100%.</p>\n<p>Y ya gastamos unos pocos para la <a href=\"/2012/tarta-de-limon\">tarta de limón</a>, que hicimos hace una semana… pero con este calor hemos empleado otros pocos para hacer una limonada.</p>\n<p>En muy poquito tiempo tienes un refresco natural y sano.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 360px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/8f967559d3881613761feb6313bae565/158ba/limonada-apm-6-pizcas.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 133.54430379746836%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"limonada apm 6 pizcas\"\n        title=\"limonada apm (6) (pizcas)\"\n        src=\"/static/8f967559d3881613761feb6313bae565/158ba/limonada-apm-6-pizcas.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8f967559d3881613761feb6313bae565/ff44c/limonada-apm-6-pizcas.jpg 158w,\n/static/8f967559d3881613761feb6313bae565/a6688/limonada-apm-6-pizcas.jpg 315w,\n/static/8f967559d3881613761feb6313bae565/158ba/limonada-apm-6-pizcas.jpg 360w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 360px) 100vw, 360px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Ingredientes:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>4 limones</li>\n<li>Corteza de un limón</li>\n<li>600 ml de agua</li>\n<li>175 gr de azúcar</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Limpiamos bien el limón que vamos a utilizar su corteza. Obtenemos la corteza y reservamos. A continuación exprimimos los 4 limones.</p>\n<p>En una jarra añadimos el agua, el zumo de los limones y el azúcar. Removemos hasta que se disuelva el azúcar. Agregamos la corteza del limón.<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 360px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d59d8a4931c22cc5ab63f4565f712264/158ba/limonada-apm-9-pizcas.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 133.54430379746836%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"limonada apm 9 pizcas\"\n        title=\"limonada apm (9) (pizcas)\"\n        src=\"/static/d59d8a4931c22cc5ab63f4565f712264/158ba/limonada-apm-9-pizcas.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d59d8a4931c22cc5ab63f4565f712264/ff44c/limonada-apm-9-pizcas.jpg 158w,\n/static/d59d8a4931c22cc5ab63f4565f712264/a6688/limonada-apm-9-pizcas.jpg 315w,\n/static/d59d8a4931c22cc5ab63f4565f712264/158ba/limonada-apm-9-pizcas.jpg 360w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 360px) 100vw, 360px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>A la hora de servirlo lo colamos y añadimos hielo para que esté bien fresquito. Y a disfrutar del calor!<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/0a30d95530652b6c023580fe40edfdc4/c08c5/limonada-apm-13-pizcas.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75.31645569620254%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"limonada apm 13 pizcas\"\n        title=\"limonada apm (13) (pizcas)\"\n        src=\"/static/0a30d95530652b6c023580fe40edfdc4/828fb/limonada-apm-13-pizcas.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/0a30d95530652b6c023580fe40edfdc4/ff44c/limonada-apm-13-pizcas.jpg 158w,\n/static/0a30d95530652b6c023580fe40edfdc4/a6688/limonada-apm-13-pizcas.jpg 315w,\n/static/0a30d95530652b6c023580fe40edfdc4/828fb/limonada-apm-13-pizcas.jpg 630w,\n/static/0a30d95530652b6c023580fe40edfdc4/c08c5/limonada-apm-13-pizcas.jpg 640w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>](/2012/limonada-pre-veraniega/limonada-apm-13-pizcas)[<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 360px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/325b261dfd80acabc5a5f0c9007bcd70/158ba/limonada-apm-14-pizcas.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 133.